data.description: **Ask for credit**Make an offer**Appraisal report dated 09/16/2023 is available, offering you a glimpse into the true value.** This house is tucked away in a peaceful cul-de-sac within the Bull Mountain neighborhood. This exquisite residence, a harmonious blend of luxury and tranquility, offers an expansive layout featuring 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, dual living areas, a basement primed for entertainment, and a cozy fireplace to gather around. In 2022, this home underwent a transformative renewal. Its exterior and interior spaces now bask in a fresh, contemporary palette. The three-car garage, enhanced with a new, low-maintenance epoxy floor, complements the home's aesthetic. Culinary dreams come to life in the fully remodeled kitchen, a masterpiece of design boasting high-end built-in appliances and an industrial-class 60" range hood. This space is an entertainer's delight, seamlessly blending functionality with style. Step onto the back patio, where natural stone elevates the outdoor experience, leading you through picturesque walkways. Inside, new hardwood floors infuse warmth throughout, while the updated landscaping, complete with low-voltage lighting and a new sprinkler system, creates an enchanting outdoor haven. The bathrooms have been rejuvenated with new floors, counters, and sleek hardware, offering a spa-like ambiance. For the movie enthusiast, the upgraded media room is a haven of entertainment, enhanced with smart features and a central vacuum system for ultimate convenience. Low-Maintenance Patio: Embrace leisure in a backyard designed for relaxation, not chores. Built-In Mini Workout: The 15 front-door steps provide a subtle, daily fitness boost. Customizable Showers: Tailor your shower experience to your personal preferences. Blank Canvas: Infuse your personality into this already stunning backdrop. For the eco-conscious, the garage is equipped with Tesla/EV charging capabilities, blending environmental responsibility with modern convenience.
